# How to make coffee

"A mathematician is a machine for turning coffee into theorems"

See https://blogs.ams.org/phdplus/2015/04/28/coffee-into-theorems/
for authorship information


## History

Nice drink was discovered from Ethiopia.

## Ingredients
- coffee
- water
- milk
- sugar
- lemon

## Where to make it
- espresso maker
- coffee machine

